I'm coming for you, beast.

1775
01:46:43,731 --> 01:46:45,642
(GRUNTING)

1776
01:46:47,610 --> 01:46:48,896
(GROWLING)

1777
01:47:00,289 --> 01:47:02,701
- No!
- Belle?

1778
01:47:07,129 --> 01:47:08,244
Belle!

1779
01:47:09,506 --> 01:47:10,541
You came back!

1780
01:47:10,716 --> 01:47:13,549
- I tried to stop them!
