1781
01:47:14,178 --> 01:47:15,178
I'm coming.

1782
01:47:16,472 --> 01:47:17,928
(GROWLING)

1783
01:47:26,482 --> 01:47:27,482
(GRUNTS)

1784
01:47:30,194 --> 01:47:31,810
(BOTH GRUNTING)

1785
01:47:38,160 --> 01:47:39,366
