Don't hurt me, beast.

1793
01:48:15,280 --> 01:48:16,896
I am not...

1794
01:48:17,074 --> 01:48:18,530
a beast.

1795
01:48:21,537 --> 01:48:23,699
- (GROWLS)
- (GRUNTS)

1796
01:48:25,290 --> 01:48:26,621
Go!

1797
01:48:27,751 --> 01:48:29,662
Get out!

1798
01:48:30,713 --> 01:48:31,874
Don't!

1799
01:48:31,964 --> 01:48:33,295
It's too far!

1800
01:48:33,465 --> 01:48:35,001
(GROWLING)

1801
01:48:43,434 --> 01:48:44,890
- (GUNSHOT)
- (ROARS)

1802
01:48:49,565 --> 01:48:50,680
BELLE: Please!

1803
01:48:53,902 --> 01:48:55,188
Come on.

1804
01:48:58,449 --> 01:49:00,406
(ROARS)

1805
01:49:06,749 --> 01:49:08,160
(WHIMPERS)

1806
01:49:09,334 --> 01:49:11,041
(SCREAMING)

1807
01:49:17,885 --> 01:49:20,627
(THE BEAST BREATHING HEAVILY)

1808
01:49:24,808 --> 01:49:26,139
You came back.

1809
01:49:27,352 --> 01:49:29,309
Of course I came back.

1810
01:49:29,480 --> 01:49:30,891
I'll never leave you again.

1811
