- Plumette?

1824
01:50:10,312 --> 01:50:11,802
Plumette?

1825
01:50:12,564 --> 01:50:15,101
Oh, my darling, Plumette.

1826
01:50:16,193 --> 01:50:17,558
Oh, no.

1827
