1844
01:51:29,683 --> 01:51:30,683
I can't...

1845
01:51:31,226 --> 01:51:32,387
Lumière...

1846
01:51:32,895 --> 01:51:33,930
my friend.

1847
01:51:34,104 --> 01:51:36,266
