1848
01:51:36,440 --> 01:51:37,521
with you.

1849
01:51:40,277 --> 01:51:42,769
The honor was mine.

1850
01:52:03,091 --> 01:52:06,504
(BELLE SOBBING)

1851
01:52:10,432 --> 01:52:11,922
Come back.

1852
01:52:12,100 --> 01:52:13,636
Please don't leave me.

1853
01:52:16,772 --> 01:52:18,979
I love you.

1854
01:52:43,006 --> 01:52:44,542
(GASPING)

1855
01:53:41,857 --> 01:53:43,518
(CHUCKLES)

1856
01:53:57,289 --> 01:53:58,575
(RUMBLING)

1857
01:54:23,899 --> 01:54:24,899
(BARKS)

1858
01:54:34,743 --> 01:54:36,825
Oh. Maestro!

1859
01:54:37,579 --> 01:54:40,788
