1866
01:55:13,573 --> 01:55:14,573
LUMIÈRE: Plumette!

1867
01:55:16,034 --> 01:55:18,025
Plumette!

1868
01:55:19,162 --> 01:55:21,699
Oh. <i>Mon amour.</i>

1869
01:55:24,626 --> 01:55:25,626
Oh.

1870
01:55:26,336 --> 01:55:28,293
