1871
01:55:31,007 --> 01:55:32,748
- (GASPS)
- Oh. Oh.

1872
01:55:37,055 --> 01:55:38,216
(BOTH WHOOPING)

1873
01:55:40,725 --> 01:55:42,466
(BOTH SHOUTING)

1874
01:55:44,354 --> 01:55:46,345
Chip! Look at you!

1875
01:55:47,190 --> 01:55:48,601
You're a little boy again!

1876
01:55:48,775 --> 01:55:50,857
What did I tell you, darling?

1877
01:55:50,986 --> 01:55:52,772
You smell so good!

1878
01:55:52,904 --> 01:55:53,904
